node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SportsCenter on August 23, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'CrossFit CrossFit @CrossFit Bob is 87 and has Parkinson's. His doctor told him to exercise and referred him to CFEA for this class. He called and showed up and has faithfully come three times a week, putting in the work. CrossFit CrossFit @CrossFit This is his first sled push and he really enjoyed it. Bob is a retired Marine Colonel and isn't about to stop! He never whines. Never complains No excuses. Displays grit and gratitude.'.
